# FILE: halabLibrary/documentReader/documentReader.desc
# ROLE: Internal Academic Viewer & Study Terminal
# ROUTE: /library/viewer/:id
# ACCOUNT: All types can view — downloads award XP to students
# THEME: Dark · distraction-free · reading-optimized

## 1. DUAL-PANE LAYOUT (12-col grid)
- COL 9 (THE VIEWER):
  - PDF.js renderer or Markdown viewer
  - Controls: Zoom +/- · Page jump · Search within doc
  - Reading mode: invert-colors toggle for ultra-dark reading
  - BG: bg-[#070C18]
- COL 3 (CONTEXT HUB):
  - METADATA: Author · Branch · Year · Verified badge
  - RELATED CONTENT: 3 suggested Shorts or Academy courses
  - AD ZONE: sidebar ad slot from admin Ad Console (if enabled)

## 2. NAVIGATION HUD (Sticky Top Bar)
- BREADCRUMB: المكتبة > [Branch] > [Document Title]
- ACTIONS:
  - [📥 تحميل الأصل] → triggers download + +25 XP for students
  - [⭐ حفظ في اللوحة] → saves to enrolled courses / bookmarks in /dashboard
  - [🔗 مشاركة الرابط]

## 3. INTERACTION LOGIC
- PROGRESS TRACKER: remembers last page read → syncs to /dashboard/learning
- FEEDBACK: "هل كان هذا الملخص مفيداً؟" Upvote / Downvote
- STUDENT XP: +25 XP on download (toast: "حصلت على +25 XP 🎉")

## 4. ACCOUNT TYPE IMPACT
- Guest: can view first 3 pages only → login CTA overlay
- Student/Business: full view + download
- Admin: full view + [🗑️ حذف المستند] [✏️ تعديل البيانات] overlay buttons
